Tga '''Ayt Mẓal''' yat taqbilt zɣ tiqbilin [[Sus|tisusiyin]]. Llan tiqbilin ad ɣ tamnaḍt n [[Tamnaḍt n Actukn-Ayt Baha|Wactukn-Ayt Baha]], s tuggugt n 70km ɣ iffus n tiɣrmt n [[Agadir|Ugadir]] ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]]. Tg '''Ayt Mẓal''' ula tagrawt, tgrawt ad gis kraḍ tqbilin ad tnt igan : Taqbilt n Ayt Mẓal, Taqbilt n Ayt Walyad, d Taqbilt n [[Agadir Imcgigiln|Imcgigiln]].

